    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The borough incorporated on March 22, 1917, after a referendum on April 12, 1917, separating from Berkeley Township.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        9,
        16
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beachwood%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 1916 a Property‑Owner’s Association formed, pushing for municipal independence that led to Beachwood’s borough status.",
